Hi Pete,
Try Evilbay and enter VW Accessory.  Just make sure to only buy and use on 
made of aluminum, and use the stock knob.  Otherwise it will get too heavy 
causing the shifter to lean more and wear out second and/or fourth shift fork 
in the tranny.
